{"article_id":"w7L8POXxoNeX2z3n","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump early Thursday pushed back on a report","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that the special counsel","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"leading the Russia probe","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"is now looking into","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"whether Trump obstructed justice .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"`` They made up a phony collusion with the Russians story ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"found zero proof ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"so now they go for obstruction of justice on the phony story .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Nice , ''","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Trump tweeted Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"They made up a phony collusion with the Russians story ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"found zero proof ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"so now they go for obstruction of justice on the phony story . Nice","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"June 15 , 2017","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"The president has in the past decried the investigation into the Russian meddling in the U.S. presidential race","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"and pushed backed against reports of collusion .","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"On Wednesday , The Washington Post reported","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"the special counsel","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"named to investigate the Russian election meddling","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"is looking into","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"whether Trump sought to obstruct justice .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The Department of Justice appointed former FBI Director Robert Mueller as special counsel","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"to oversee the Russia probe shortly after Trump 's decision","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"to fire former FBI Director James Comey .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Trump claimed","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"- and Comey later affirmed -","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that Comey assured him","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"he was not personally under FBI investigation .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"But investigators began probing Trump for obstruction of justice soon after Comey ' s termination .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"After Comey 's testimony last week , further questions were raised","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"about whether Trump tried to obstruct justice .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"The Thursday morning tweet was Trump 's first about the investigation since the shooting Wednesday at a congressional baseball practice in Alexandria , Va. ,","depth":3},{"id":34,"text":"in which House Majority Whip Steve Scalise","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"( R-La . )","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"was critically injured .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"Trump after the shooting called for unity in a statement","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"delivered at the White House .","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"\" We may have our differences ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"but we do well in times like these to remember","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"everyone","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who serves in our nation ' s capital","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"is here","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"because , above all , they love our country , \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"\" We can all agree","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"that we are blessed to be Americans ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"that our children deserve to grow up in a nation of safety and peace","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"and we are strongest","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"when we are unified","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and when we work together for the common good . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":103,"left":84,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":67,"right":83,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":56,"right":66,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":56,"left":0,"right":55,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},